    <section class="glass p-5">
      <h2 class="font-semibold mb-3"><Bilingual><span slot="zh">C++20 协程：异步模型对比</span><span slot="en">C++20 Coroutines: Async Model Comparison</span></Bilingual></h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-ink-muted mb-3"><Bilingual><span slot="zh"><b>协程</b>是可暂停-恢复的函数——<code>co_await</code> 挂起不阻塞线程，<code>co_yield</code> 产出值，<code>co_return</code> 完成。相比线程，协程<b>无栈、极轻量</b>（KB 级 vs MB 级），适合异步 I/O、生成器、状态机。C++20 协程是<b>编译器特性</b>——需要库提供 <code>promise_type</code>，标准库的 <code>std::generator</code>（C++23）和第三方 <code>cppcoro</code> 提供常用设施。</span><span slot="en"><b>Coroutines</b> are suspendable-resumable functions — <code>co_await</code> suspends without blocking the thread, <code>co_yield</code> produces a value, <code>co_return</code> finishes. Compared to threads, coroutines are <b>stackless, extremely lightweight</b> (KB vs MB), ideal for async I/O, generators, state machines. C++20 coroutines are a <b>compiler feature</b> — libraries provide <code>promise_type</code>; <code>std::generator</code> (C++23) and third-party <code>cppcoro</code> provide common facilities.</span></Bilingual></p>
